    • Field Detail

      • DEFAULT_TYPE

        public static final java.lang.String DEFAULT_TYPE
        Represents the default type for command elements matched by FLAG or ARGUMENT. If no type is defined in those matches, this value is used. 'String' is used as this is the base value provided to Selene, thus requiring no further converting to other data types.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
